msgid "# Decode Context Parallel Guide"
msgstr "# 解码上下文并行指南"

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid ""
"Decode Context Parallel (DCP) shards the KV cache along the sequence "
"dimension across devices in a Tensor Parallel (TP) group. It removes "
"redundant KV-cache copies and can increase the batch size available for "
"long-context decoding."
msgstr ""
"解码上下文并行（DCP）在张量并行（TP）组内沿序列维度将 KV 缓存分片到不同设备，"
"从而消除重复的 KV 缓存副本，并可增大长上下文解码可用的批大小。"

msgid ""
"Prefill Context Parallel is not supported by vLLM Ascend. The upstream "
"`prefill_context_parallel_size` option must remain at its default value of "
"`1`."
msgstr ""
"vLLM Ascend 不支持预填充上下文并行。上游的 "
"`prefill_context_parallel_size` 选项必须保持默认值 `1`。"

